dataset.description: A list of hospital outpatient department ratings for the Outpatient and Ambulatory Surgery Consumer Assessment of Healthcare Providers and Systems (OAS CAHPS) survey. The data are updated and reported each quarter with data from the most recently completed quarter replacing the oldest quarter of data. The data reporting period is included in the tables.
dataset.title: Outpatient and Ambulatory Surgery Consumer Assessment of Healthcare Providers and Systems (OAS CAHPS) survey for hospital outpatient departments - Facility
